    {
      "text": "Party Time with Winnie the Pooh (known as Pooh's Party Game: In Search of the Treasure in North America) is a 2001 party video game developed by Doki Denki for the PlayStation. It was released by Electronic Arts in the United States and Sony Computer Entertainment in Europe. Disney Interactive released the game on Windows.\nIt was released as a PlayStation Classic for the PlayStation 3 and PlayStation Portable via the PlayStation Store on 13 September 2009.",
